== Tavutomi byakwe ==
=== Malembe yosungula na tidyondzo ===
Marivate unghene xikolo eValdezia primary school (lexi akiweke hi lembe ra 1888) ekusuhi na Louis Trichardt eNorthern Transvaal (laha namunthla kunga xifundzha xa Limpopo), na Lemana Training Institution.{{kulaveka vumbhoni}} 

=== Tidyondzo tale henhla na vufundhisi: ===
Hi lembe ra 1897 Cornelius Marivate uvekiwe kuva mupfuni wa Mufundhisi Malale, xikan'we na Joshua Marule na Frank Hlaise. Hikufamba ka nkarhi Marivate uvile mufundhisi wa kereke ya Tsonga Presbyterian (Kumbe Swiss Mission) andzhawuni ya vurhumiwa ya Valdezia.{{kulaveka vumbhoni}} 

=== Vutsari na maphepha-hungu: ===
Marivate uthlele ava muhleri phephahungu ra muganga, ra The Valdezia Bulletin/Light, xikan'we  na E.A. Tlakula and A.E. Mpapele. Phephahungu lere ri gandlisiwe no haxiva kwalomu ka malembe ya nkombo kufikela laha ringa yimisiwa.{{kulaveka vumbhoni}} 

